Bug Hall https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bug_Hall 0 Brandon "Bug" Hall (born February 4, 1985) is an American actor. He is best known for his childhood roles as Alfalfa in The Little Rascals (1994) and Buster Stupid in The Stupids (1996). Brandon_"_Bug_"_Hall ( born February_4_,_1985 ) is an_American_actor .
